<i>Não!</i>

882
01:22:58,680 --> 01:22:59,639
<i>Nós...</i>

883
01:27:16,406 --> 01:27:17,991
Me dê isso!

884
01:28:51,422 --> 01:28:53,174
Você e eu...

885
01:28:54,425 --> 01:28:57,429
acho que não seguimos
a mesma linha.

886
01:29:34,008 --> 01:29:35,718
Ray! Ray!

887
01:29:35,718 --> 01:29:36,594
Ray! Ray!

888
01:29:36,803 --> 01:29:39,514
Ray! Ray! Ray!

889
01:29:41,432 --> 01:29:44,310
